metadata.name: LovE,DeatH & WeB3 - ParT 1
metadata.description:
In the heart of a man, there lived love and strife  
One an angel, the other a devil in life  
The angel of love, with a halo of gold  
Brought joy and peace, to the heart that he's hold

He whispered of kindness, and spoke of the truth  
Guided the man, with a sense of proof  
With a smile, and a gentle touch  
The angel of love, brought love, as such

The devil of strife, with horns on his head  
Brought chaos and turmoil, to the man who was led  
He tempted the man, with desires and fears  
And whispered of greed, in his ear

And so the man chose, the path of the light  
And banished the devil, from his sight  
He followed the angel, and held love so tight
